  <summary>A polished modernization of the original Master of Orion Strategy game from 1993.</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Remnants of the Precursors is a modernization of the 1993 strategy game "Master of Orion".
      You will play as one of 10 unique races and lead them to galactic domination or, if you fail,
      humiliation and defeat. Micromanagement is minimal and the gameplay smooth and streamlined.</p>
  </description>

